<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc4157ae8-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87" identifier="/us/usc/t38/s7621"><num value="7621">§ 7621.</num><heading> Authority for program</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As part of the Educational Assistance Program, the Secretary shall carry out a tuition reimbursement program under this subchapter. The program shall be known as the Department of Veterans Affairs Nurse Education Tuition Reimbursement Program (hereinafter in this chapter referred to as the “Tuition Reimbursement Program”).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc4157ae9-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/100/322/tII/s216/b">Pub. L. 100–322, title II, § 216(b)</ref>, <date date="1988-05-20">May 20, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/525">102 Stat. 525</ref>, § 4321; renumbered § 7621, <ref href="/us/pl/102/40/tIV/s402/b/1">Pub. L. 102–40, title IV, § 402(b)(1)</ref>, <date date="1991-05-07">May 7, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/238">105 Stat. 238</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/102/83/s4/a/2/B/vi">Pub. L. 102–83, § 4(a)(2)(B)(vi)</ref>, (b)(1), (2)(E), <date date="1991-08-06">Aug. 6, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/403-405">105 Stat. 403–405</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idc4157aea-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">
